put.description:
Use this format for changing or not changing formulas and annotations:

``` json
"formulas": {
    "dsUpdated": [],
    "dsDeleted": [],
     "card": []
},
"annotations": {
    "new": [],
    "modified": [],
     "deleted": []
},

 ```

For conditionalFormats, change the array to an object and separate out DataSet vs. Card rules:

``` json
"conditionalFormats": {
    "card": [],
     "datasource": []
},

 ```

If copying from the Get Card Detaisls for Update endpoint, remove everything on the top-level except definition. Then add dataProvider and variables:

``` json
{
    "definition": {
...},
    "dataProvider": {
        "dataSourceId": "1dbaba48-da44-4e13-a3e6-53432cf1ae7c"
    },
    "variables": true
}

 ```

